column2: SELECT   count(xm.wise_cntr) as wise_xmatch_count,count(xm.sdss_objid) as sdss_xmatch_count, avg(w.w1mpro) as w1_mean, max(w.w1mpro) as w1_max into mydb.MyTable_# from wise_xmatch as xm     left join photoObjAll as p on xm.sdss_objid = p.objid     left join wise_allsky as w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr
